reviewText: QUALITY DVD. WILL BE ENJOYED BY ALL WHO VIEW IT.

I was unsure about getting this dvd, But I am glad that I did. the show is informative and interesting with lots of good footage and narration
I put this on at my friends party and it drew all the car guys and girls there like a magnet.
I will be buying the rest of the series thumbs up.
Great interviews with the original 'Ramchargers'.  Great mix of vintage and mordern footage. Definately an entertaining and informative history of one of muscle cars formative drag racing teams.
